enb_long_title: Eleventh Session of The INC for the Framework Convention on Climate Change (UNFCCC)
sentences: The Plenary met at 4:00 pm in an informal session to discuss the Rules of Procedure.
Sreenivasan, distributed two non-papers from Monday`s drafting group.
The first contains the bracketed rules and the second one contains new proposals.
Rule 6 (Observers) and Rule 27 (Subsidiary Bodies) were accepted.
